<CollClass name="ArrayOfHugeStringArray" id="7e71872d-54f8-4d9b-88fd-fde9124f97dc">
    <memberType name="HugeStringArray"/>
    <superclass name="Array"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>This class is to store strings longer than 2048(mostly used for REST responses). 
This class has an array, each of which is a response that could be more than 
2048 chars long. To read a complete response, all of the HugeStrs in the 
HugeStrArray in a single index of ArrayOfHugeStrArray need to be concatinated.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="_environ"/>
</CollClass>
